| --- | --- |
| `@motion-core/motion-gpu` | Framework-agnostic core runtime primitives (`defineMaterial`, `createFrameRegistry`, `createMotionGPURuntimeLoop`, `createCurrentWritable`, passes incl. `ComputePass`/`PingPongComputePass`, texture loader, error normalization) |
| `@motion-core/motion-gpu/advanced` | Core runtime plus scheduler helper utilities (`applySchedulerPreset`, `captureSchedulerDebugSnapshot`) |
